                        <p>MVP is one of the most discussed concepts in mobility space. Mostly used by startups, the concept of Minimum Viable Product increases the chances of success with their products on the market.</p>
                        <p>Software development companies used to spend years building a stable product for release it to its customers. With technology moving so fast and methods like Agile
